{"tid":1537303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中国踐踏港人權利 德報：歐盟可考慮與台建交","createTime":"2019-09-04T01:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:42:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":371,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"42881416377142333afa740f83fcc248faa4794e","tid":1537303,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:20:21.000Z","msg":"德國總理梅克爾即將出訪北京，德國大報「世界報」建議她向北京清楚表達保障港人權利的立場，如果中國不接受，歐盟可考慮與台灣建交。<br />\n<br />\n德國「世界報」（Die Welt）集團總主筆舒斯特（Jacques Schuster）批評，德國經常教訓美國等盟邦，對他們有道德優越感；在中國這樣的巨人前卻通常只是閃躲。外長馬斯（Heiko Maas）評論香港局勢，「情勢持續惡化，我們呼籲各方都要讓步」，等於什麼也沒說。<br />\n<br />\n舒斯特在這篇2日刊出的社論指出，香港天天都有人在街上被拖進秘密警察的車和丟進牢裡，只因他們勇於提醒北京1984年「中英聯合聲明」賦予他們的權利。德國官員只會呼籲、建議和要求各方冷靜，彷彿這是一場勢均力敵、雙方也該負一樣責任的對抗。<br />\n<br />\n舒斯特認為，歐盟面對中國時習慣自我矮化，導致中國領導人一點也不把歐洲放在眼裡。事實上，歐盟已經壯大到可以對北京明白表示，極權政府對香港的任何一步都將付出代價。如果中國連在中英聯合聲明保證的港人權利都無法忍受的話，歐盟手中還有其他政治武器，那就是與台灣建立外交關係，並承認達賴喇嘛為西藏的國家領袖。<br />\n<br />\n舒斯特指出，如果走到這一步，歐洲應該賦予港人難民地位和公民身分，因為港人對自由表現出的渴望和勇氣，讓人毫不懷疑他們將為歐洲和西方世界帶來好處。<br />\n<br />\n「商報」（Handelsblatt）4日在社論中也指出，長期來看，對北京卑躬屈膝從來就不值得，只會增加被當成肥羊宰殺的危險。<br />\n<br />\n商報認為，不論是社會信用體系或在企業內成立黨支部，外商在中國面臨的政治壓力愈來愈大。為了本國企業的利益，梅克爾應該把握機會，向北京領導人明白表示反對鎮壓香港。<br />\n<br />\n根據德國政府公布的行程，梅克爾6日將與中國國務院總理李克強共進早餐和面對媒體，晚上與中國國家主席習近平共進晚餐。這是她13年總理任內第12度造訪中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4027501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F4027501&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3BURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=de18083c\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4027501</a>"},{"pid":"83bfd9751e1121a59c2cfaacbef3627dac9174f8","tid":1537303,"uid":29880,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:21:06.000Z","msg":"聽住先"},{"pid":"271d1a9054c598848c3116dfa6ee23555ee08b09","tid":1537303,"uid":257422,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:21:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">(集中討論) <br />\n908 九月八日<br />\n<br />\n12:30pm<br />\n <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">遮打花園</span> <br />\n或 <br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">愛丁堡廣場</span> <br />\n集合<br />\n<br />\n2:00pm <br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">美國駐港澳總領事館</span><br />\n<br />\n《香港人權及民主法案》集會請願 ! ! <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">扯國旗!</span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">唱國歌 !</span></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536086\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536086</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/kCGOYms.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCGOYms.jpg&h=ced74507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/JGPEpwY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJGPEpwY.jpg&h=115c89d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽歌隨意門(附歌詞):</span></span><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3BURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=23e0e564\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">手足動人獻唱自由國度之歌</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNfTjAM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNfTjAM.gif&h=db1663f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3BURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=8218b13f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a>"},{"pid":"89d28ce0637450dbfd1f8ae85d67f98fce289198","tid":1537303,"uid":177089,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:23:49.000Z","msg":"北大西洋公約國 全球反共民主聯合戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a554737bd81938462b79b6b4865cee3e811e16ac","tid":1537303,"uid":221100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:24:23.000Z","msg":"Sir , this way"},{"pid":"05cc22eed38d1525039894e3b95d6f8e6496c0d4","tid":1537303,"uid":30510,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:26:49.000Z","msg":"Sir, auf diese weise"},{"pid":"5ef6721f86e9b32dbdf9de30953e34391ba30d1b","tid":1537303,"uid":211461,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:27:33.000Z","msg":"只係德國其中一份報紙既一篇社論"},{"pid":"0ac00b0375de04dacd3b482837d4b8c2d9b65cf3","tid":1537303,"uid":137217,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:28:34.000Z","msg":"條左膠夠閪膽反共咩<br />\n奶共就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇英國就知"},{"pid":"543528e9045172360fad31aca98943e26771f825","tid":1537303,"uid":237562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0ac00b0375de04dacd3b482837d4b8c2d9b65cf3","tid":1537303,"uid":137217,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:28:34.000Z","msg":"條左膠夠閪膽反共咩<br />\n奶共就叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇英國就知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:30:33.000Z","msg":"美國民主黨呢?"},{"pid":"212fc0fe17f73a7aecbc48bd379f081499e55561","tid":1537303,"uid":197976,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"可惜只係報紙社評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當初歐美根本唔應該承認中共地位放棄台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申到今日都原諒唔到左膠美國總統卡特同中華民國斷交<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ad538c8187cf7fcb5ae98922efa2401471ce21","tid":1537303,"uid":199640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"05cc22eed38d1525039894e3b95d6f8e6496c0d4","tid":1537303,"uid":30510,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:26:49.000Z","msg":"Sir, auf diese weise"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:32:28.000Z","msg":"Herren, auf diese weise"},{"pid":"7911841a6e56a72cfae47046d6bb3b66a217dfcb","tid":1537303,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:33:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0aa3c89add5ffb026f7459dadfb15adef55bed1","tid":1537303,"uid":137217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:33:48.000Z","msg":"起碼e家民主黨話對中國政策兩黨係有共識一齊隊佢先"},{"pid":"cf6b90af6ad86c055091bddb43dac51af85c02e9","tid":1537303,"uid":120431,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e9f8ff11925c6e9ab24fff58f45b421f8fd971","tid":1537303,"uid":108347,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:36:41.000Z","msg":"外國戰線初見成效，大家咪爭住認輸，分分鍾打到下年"},{"pid":"1d74423e61f9cbfd1bd0ab0e3c79e231c342ef78","tid":1537303,"uid":21432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:37:21.000Z","msg":"歐洲人要訓醒仲有好長既路，波羅的海三國係因為曾經有同樣遭遇所以更有認同感。<br />\n個人對默克爾政權十分失望，典型對錢跪類型，馬克龍有的表現反而令人有少少期待。"},{"pid":"d75c31ebff6657a2f6cc55d434595a74b5e55c3b","tid":1537303,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快d收中共皮"},{"pid":"2b920a49ae35c205d5d1d51236fa98060212e217","tid":1537303,"uid":2654,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:40:22.000Z","msg":"因為港人對自由表現出的渴望和勇氣，讓人毫不懷疑他們將為歐洲和西方世界帶來好處。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953ea36bfb30a6a107accb609bdcbfd8458a38e4","tid":1537303,"uid":35914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:42:09.000Z","msg":"希望唔會淨係口講<br />\n幫到臺灣十分支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0780e36805600974e6ebfbcb3488fb28e971e021","tid":1537303,"uid":2654,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:43:07.000Z","msg":"中國人呢個賤種民族，你要開隻窗，就話要開個屋頂，所以你一同台灣傾建交自然會含你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9777fa175f91f3b6007dda7a496c2487f9be0f68","tid":1537303,"uid":9315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d75c31ebff6657a2f6cc55d434595a74b5e55c3b","tid":1537303,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快d收中共皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:45:30.000Z","msg":"到時實打台灣黎轉移視線  煽動中國人  製造偽國難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果到時美國同其他盟友冇決心對付  台灣就係咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e80ca258f41eabfb7f407e4d86e01fe5ca626b","tid":1537303,"uid":284870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f23b7c92e720f38ccc79660121acce51277d803","tid":1537303,"uid":202571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42881416377142333afa740f83fcc248faa4794e","tid":1537303,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:20:21.000Z","msg":"德國總理梅克爾即將出訪北京，德國大報「世界報」建議她向北京清楚表達保障港人權利的立場，如果中國不接受，歐盟可考慮與台灣建交。<br />\n<br />\n德國「世界報」（Die Welt）集團總主筆舒斯特（Jacques Schuster）批評，德國經常教訓美國等盟邦，對他們有道德優越感；在中國這樣的巨人前卻通常只是閃躲。外長馬斯（Heiko Maas）評論香港局勢，「情勢持續惡化，我們呼籲各方都要讓步」，等於什麼也沒說。<br />\n<br />\n舒斯特在這篇2日刊出的社論指出，香港天天都有人在街上被拖進秘密警察的車和丟進牢裡，只因他們勇於提醒北京1984年「中英聯合聲明」賦予他們的權利。德國官員只會呼籲、建議和要求各方冷靜，彷彿這是一場勢均力敵、雙方也該負一樣責任的對抗。<br />\n<br />\n舒斯特認為，歐盟面對中國時習慣自我矮化，導致中國領導人一點也不把歐洲放在眼裡。事實上，歐盟已經壯大到可以對北京明白表示，極權政府對香港的任何一步都將付出代價。如果中國連在中英聯合聲明保證的港人權利都無法忍受的話，歐盟手中還有其他政治武器，那就是與台灣建立外交關係，並承認達賴喇嘛為西藏的國家領袖。<br />\n<br />\n舒斯特指出，如果走到這一步，歐洲應該賦予港人難民地位和公民身分，因為港人對自由表現出的渴望和勇氣，讓人毫不懷疑他們將為歐洲和西方世界帶來好處。<br />\n<br />\n「商報」（Handelsblatt）4日在社論中也指出，長期來看，對北京卑躬屈膝從來就不值得，只會增加被當成肥羊宰殺的危險。<br />\n<br />\n商報認為，不論是社會信用體系或在企業內成立黨支部，外商在中國面臨的政治壓力愈來愈大。為了本國企業的利益，梅克爾應該把握機會，向北京領導人明白表示反對鎮壓香港。<br />\n<br />\n根據德國政府公布的行程，梅克爾6日將與中國國務院總理李克強共進早餐和面對媒體，晚上與中國國家主席習近平共進晚餐。這是她13年總理任內第12度造訪中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4027501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F4027501&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3BURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=de18083c\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4027501</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:48:58.000Z","msg":"建議用歐盟-中華民國關係建交，重新承認中華民國代表中國地位<br />\n等中共慢慢失去大陸控制權<br />\n由國民政府頂上"},{"pid":"531274ad86fbda1dae597523e661dcd781999bb5","tid":1537303,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T01:53:02.000Z","msg":"社論&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39dfdf3b77c9acf0781734bb627bb00e5c